events.text:
When that bastard Killrok left our clan he took a good amount of us with him down south.
He broke pack with our Chieftain and spilled blood in this sacred land. Such treason will not be tolerated.
There is an outstanding bounty on Killrok's head. If you just manage to bring it to me, Nur Murk will reward you handsomely.

So the dreaded killrok is dead? Good riddance. You've proven yourself in battle.
Such word will be sent back to Khozgrogal of your doings.
